1
00:00:00,100 --> 00:00:05,501
Use collaboration mode when the destination matters, but the route needs repeated human judgment.

2
00:00:05,451 --> 00:00:07,480
Both sides stay active.

3
00:00:07,480 --> 00:00:15,461
The AI proposes, transforms, or checks; the human selects, redirects, and supplies context the system cannot infer.

4
00:00:15,461 --> 00:00:18,721
Collaboration works best around a shared artifact.

5
00:00:18,721 --> 00:00:22,932
Edit the actual brief, code path, model, or storyboard.

6
00:00:22,932 --> 00:00:30,326
A concrete artifact turns taste into visible decisions and prevents the conversation from becoming an abstract stream of suggestions.

7
00:00:30,326 --> 00:00:32,125
Work in short loops.

8
00:00:32,125 --> 00:00:37,387
Ask for one meaningful change, inspect the result, and state what improved or failed.

9
00:00:37,387 --> 00:00:43,971
The next instruction should update the artifact and the acceptance criteria, not restart the whole task from a blank prompt.

10
00:00:43,971 --> 00:00:51,528
This mode is powerful for writing, design, diagnosis, planning, and code review because quality emerges through contrast.

11
00:00:51,528 --> 00:00:57,298
The AI can generate options quickly, but the human decides which tradeoff belongs in the final result.

12
00:00:57,298 --> 00:01:00,211
The common failure is invisible convergence.

13
00:01:00,211 --> 00:01:04,894
The conversation feels productive, yet nobody can say what “done” means.

14
00:01:04,894 --> 00:01:13,019
Keep a small scorecard: audience, purpose, constraints, must-keep facts, and the test that determines whether the artifact is acceptable.

15
00:01:13,019 --> 00:01:17,144
Collaboration ends when the next steps become mechanical and checkable.

16
00:01:17,144 --> 00:01:20,721
At that point, package the remaining work for delegation.

17
00:01:20,721 --> 00:01:27,000
If the artifact still has competing directions, stay in collaboration or move briefly into exploration.

18
00:01:27,000 --> 00:01:30,990
First, Collaborate when judgment improves every iteration.

19
00:01:30,990 --> 00:01:34,855
Second, Share a live artifact instead of abstract chat.

20
00:01:34,855 --> 00:01:37,807
Third, Keep acceptance criteria visible.
